This is a side-scrolling shooter game made in two chapters.
We will explain each file.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
START.BAT

When you run this, the game will start, and when you press break it will end.

If the game won't start, it may be due to a strange environment or you've held down break.
In the latter case, you may be able to play the game by pressing break once and then starting.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
SHOOT.X

This is an executable file.
Usually executed in START.BAT
------------------------------------------------------------------------
BOSS.SP SHOOT.SP STAGE1.SP

The sprite pattern data used in this game, stage1.sp and boss.sp, 
are read in the program and written to the PCG data area when necessary.

SHOOT.PAL

Palette data for sprites.
shoot.sp and shoot.pal must be loaded into the sprite area before running shoot.x.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
SOUND.ZMD START.ZMD 1ST.ZMD 2ND.ZMD 3RD.ZMD BOSS.ZMD
SOUND01.ZMD SOUND02.ZMD SOUND03.ZMD SOUND04.ZMD SOUND05.ZMD SOUND06.ZMD

Sound effects and background music data files. Playable with zmusic.

SHOOT.ZPD

ADPCM data file for the above BGM
------------------------------------------------------------------------
STAGE1.BG STAGE2.BG STAGE3.BG

This is the background pattern data for each stage. You can edit it with BGED.X.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
TITLE.DAT

This is the title graphic data. It is a 65536 color solid data.
